{"tid":1940879,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"弘立書院違停學令－－－我相信唔係個別事件，歡迎篤灰","createTime":"2020-03-24T05:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T00:16:30.000Z","uid":169262,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a0fde67182fa981d7093194c927ee2660af8000","tid":1940879,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】弘立書院違停學令 非畢業班學生照返學<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情下全港停課，教育局早前容許國際學校「彈性」為即將參加公開試的學生進行「必需的小組學習」，其後又發稿「澄清」安排只適用於畢業班，並非容許彈性復課。《蘋果》獲悉，弘立書院於上周一（16日）起已同時容許明年和後年才畢業的學生回校，提供「小組導修課」，有家長透露過百學生回校全班上課，師生上課時咳嗽卻不戴口罩。教育局未有正面回應該校有否違規，僅稱會向學校了解詳情，並因應情況提供意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/UDA6YY5PQDII2YBEVCRIDQRW5E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_InOneFamily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR13Q2U8WPYWvelIuxf02iGG08YfZtnCxhMW3dRaKSvlIYqweo44YnRDTTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FUDA6YY5PQDII2YBEVCRIDQRW5E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_InOneFamily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR13Q2U8WPYWvelIuxf02iGG08YfZtnCxhMW3dRaKSvlIYqweo44YnRDTTg&d=%2BQAufOe15lwSrakhKFXs1mdKmUD4oZ9Yq66eb74BBG8%3D&h=9bf30bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200324%2FUDA6YY5PQDII2YBEVCRIDQRW5E%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_InOneFamily%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR13Q2U8WPYWvelIuxf02iGG08YfZtnCxhMW3dRaKSvlIYqweo44YnRDTTg&h=6ecf6582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200324/UDA6YY5PQDII2YBEVCRIDQRW5E/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_InOneFamily&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR13Q2U8WPYWvelIuxf02iGG08YfZtnCxhMW3dRaKSvlIYqweo44YnRDTTg</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎篤灰</span></strong>